SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]

) AS [t]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

) AS [t]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CardGuid], [c].[CityId], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id], [s].[Name], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Name], [c0].[StateId], [c1].[Id], [c1].[Name]
FROM [Community] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN [State] AS [s] ON [c].[StateId] = [s].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [City] AS [c0] ON [c].[CityId] = [c0].[Id]

ORDER BY [c].[Id] DESC

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]

) AS [t]

OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]

) AS [t]

WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

2025-05-17 01:47:28.410 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (33ms) [Parameters=[@__roleId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]

    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

2025-05-17 11:13:50.240 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (33ms) [Parameters=[@__roleId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'

OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Name], [m].[Url], [t].[SubmenuId], [t].[SubmenuName], [t].[Url], [t].[Id]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
OUTER APPLY (
    SELECT [m0].[Id] AS [SubmenuId], COALESCE([m0].[Name], N'') AS [SubmenuName], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [m1].[Url]
        FROM [Menu] AS [m1]
        WHERE [m1].[Id] = [m0].[Id]) AS [Url], [r].[Id]
    FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Menu] AS [m0] ON [r].[SubMenuId] = [m0].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[RoleId] = @__roleId_0 AND [m].[Id] = [r].[MenuId]
) AS [t]
WHERE [m].[ParentId] = N'0'
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [v].[Id], [v].[BlockNo], [v].[CommunityId], [v].[ContactPerson1], [v].[ContactPerson2], [v].[CreatedBy], [v].[CreatedDate], [v].[EntryTime], [v].[ExitTime], [v].[HouseNo], [v].[LevelNo], [v].[RoadNo], [v].[Status], [v].[UpdatedBy], [v].[UpdatedDate], [v].[VehicleNo], [v].[VisitPurpose], [v].[VisitorAccessTypeId], [v].[VisitorName], [v0].[Id], [v0].[CreatedBy], [v0].[CreatedDate], [v0].[Name], [v0].[UpdatedBy], [v0].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CardGuid], [c].[CityId], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate]
FROM [VisitorAccessDetails] AS [v]
LEFT JOIN [VisitorAccessType] AS [v0] ON [v].[VisitorAccessTypeId] = [v0].[Id]
